{"id":"20260616132906.225903900","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"安装完成。新增 13 个 taste 技能：\n\n| 技能 | 作用 |\n|---|---|\n| `taste-skill` | 核心 — 品味/设计感判断 |\n| `taste-skill-v1` | 旧版 taste |\n| `brandkit` | 品牌工具包 |\n| `brutalist-skill` | 粗野主义风格 |\n| `minimalist-skill` | 极简风格 |\n| `soft-skill` | 柔和风格 |\n| `image-to-code-skill` | 图片转代码 |\n| `imagegen-frontend-mobile` | 移动端前端生成 |\n| `imagegen-frontend-web` | Web 前端生成 |\n| `redesign-skill` | 重新设计 |\n| `stitch-skill` | 拼接/组合 |\n| `output-skill` | 输出格式化 |\n| `gpt-tasteskill` | GPT 版 taste |\n\n项目现在共 50 个技能。需要我做什么？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"DeepSeek-V4-Pro","responseId":"chatcmpl-d7614039-9c22-4497-8a04-0956ebb3b64e","usage":{"input":6831,"output":215,"totalTokens":7046,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":"2026-06-16T13:28:56.0490219+08:00"},"messageRole":"assistant","timestamp":"2026-06-16T13:28:56.0490219+08:00","type":"message"}
