{"id":"20260616133111.582978000","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"项目 `skills/` 目录下目前共 **51 个技能**（文件夹数）。\n\n不过你问的是\"对话记录\"——你需要的是什么？是指：\n\n1. 当前对话的历史记录条数？\n2. 某个文件/日志中的对话记录？\n3. 别的东西？\n\n请明确一下，我好精准回答。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"DeepSeek-V4-Pro","responseId":"chatcmpl-29657f51-e5a8-417c-99f8-dfac90bdee4d","usage":{"input":6617,"output":70,"totalTokens":6687,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":"2026-06-16T13:31:10.5380402+08:00"},"messageRole":"assistant","timestamp":"2026-06-16T13:31:10.5380402+08:00","type":"message"}
